WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:02.657
- Previously, on The Originals...
- You're a wolf. Why aren't you healing?

00:02.659 --> 00:04.882
A monster is still a
biological organism.

00:04.885 --> 00:06.634
- So, I devised a treatment.
- If you found

00:06.637 --> 00:07.903
a way to weaken yourself,

00:07.906 --> 00:09.206
maybe you can

00:09.208 --> 00:10.828
help me find a way
to kill Marcel Gerard.

00:10.831 --> 00:12.531
Maxine. It's Adam.

00:12.534 --> 00:14.979
He never came home.

00:14.981 --> 00:16.501
Adam Folsom was your only case.

00:16.504 --> 00:18.349
We got three additional
reports of missing kids.

00:18.351 --> 00:19.684
Eight years ago, you were running

00:19.686 --> 00:21.052
this city with an iron fist.

00:21.054 --> 00:22.653
I start looking for forms of magic

00:22.655 --> 00:24.221
that you can't defend against.

00:24.223 --> 00:25.423
Sacrificial magic.

00:25.425 --> 00:26.824
You freed it, Vincent.

00:26.826 --> 00:28.793
And now, it must be fed.

00:28.795 --> 00:30.261
I'm so cold.

00:30.263 --> 00:33.264
That witch, he used their personal items

00:33.266 --> 00:34.465
to bind them to the spell.

00:34.467 --> 00:36.467
Hope Mikaelson is linked to that spell.

00:36.469 --> 00:38.502
She's gonna die. We got
to cast a cleansing spell

00:38.504 --> 00:40.071
on New Orleans soil.

00:40.073 --> 00:41.706
Paramedics took the kids

00:41.708 --> 00:43.391
to the hospital to
get checked out.

00:43.394 --> 00:44.942
NOLA PD will notify the parents.

