00:55.922 --> 00:57.621
Hell of a sight.

00:57.623 --> 01:00.491
Powerful man overlooking his city.

01:02.428 --> 01:05.930
I wonder if I could convince
you to change your view?

01:05.932 --> 01:09.500
Oh, not that you aren't
stunning, 'cause you are,

01:09.502 --> 01:11.836
I'm just, um...

01:11.838 --> 01:14.205
I'm having trouble shaking
off the day that I had.

01:14.207 --> 01:16.374
So...

01:16.376 --> 01:19.844
you're saying you
could use a distraction?

01:19.846 --> 01:22.046
Allow me to distract.

01:25.351 --> 01:27.418
Mm.

01:30.911 --> 01:32.911
Just ignore it.

01:32.914 --> 01:35.993
No, just one second.

01:37.196 --> 01:39.363
Yeah. All right.

01:41.167 --> 01:42.933
Come in...

01:48.374 --> 01:50.341
Marcel, we got a problem.

01:51.054 --> 01:53.321
Those kids. They never made it home.

01:53.324 --> 01:55.179
What are you talking
about? I loaded those kids

01:55.181 --> 01:56.480
into the ambulance myself.

01:56.482 --> 01:59.216
The ambulance is missing too.

02:23.242 --> 02:25.142
The children are sedated.

02:25.144 --> 02:27.299
I've already prepared them.

02:27.302 --> 02:28.369
For the rich'll.

02:31.184 --> 02:33.150
A token of our master's power.

02:33.152 --> 02:36.053
You'll need it for what's to come.

02:37.790 --> 02:40.324
Just one last thing.

02:40.326 --> 02:41.792
Your friend.

02:41.794 --> 02:43.327
Vincent Griffith.

02:43.329 --> 02:45.896
I won't let anything stop us.

02:47.166 --> 02:48.699
Our home.

02:48.701 --> 02:51.135
Once the pride of our
family, now a flophouse.

02:51.137 --> 02:52.770
Indeed, the mighty have fallen.

02:52.772 --> 02:53.771
Where's Vincent?

02:53.773 --> 02:55.906
Right here.

02:55.908 --> 02:57.254
Kept my word.

02:57.257 --> 02:59.157
Now the only question is whether or not

02:59.160 --> 03:01.079
you guys are gonna keep
yours. As soon as I'm finished

03:01.081 --> 03:03.295
healing your kid, you
got to leave the city.

03:03.298 --> 03:04.882
Well, we're not gonna stay, are we?

03:04.884 --> 03:06.784
Your city has lost its charm.

03:06.786 --> 03:10.154
What he means to say is that
we're very grateful, just...

03:10.156 --> 03:11.489
help her and we'll leave.

03:11.491 --> 03:13.424
Just give us what we need,

03:13.426 --> 03:15.259
and we will do so, happily.

03:15.261 --> 03:16.927
Excuse me.

03:18.598 --> 03:20.865
Okay...

03:23.803 --> 03:26.270
Nettoyer timoun sa a.

03:27.673 --> 03:30.341
Nettoyer timoun.

03:31.844 --> 03:34.612
Nettoyer timoun sa a.

03:34.614 --> 03:37.681
Nettoyer...

03:44.624 --> 03:46.457
Oh...

03:46.459 --> 03:47.725
Mom?

03:47.727 --> 03:49.994
- That's it.
- Oh!

03:49.996 --> 03:52.863
- Your little girl's purified.
- Thank you.

03:52.865 --> 03:55.099
Now look, the only gratitude
I need from any of you

03:55.101 --> 03:56.834
is seeing you leave the city.

03:59.690 --> 04:03.274
Go see your daddy.

04:14.336 --> 04:15.686
What is this?

04:15.688 --> 04:16.720
I don't know.

04:18.858 --> 04:20.991
Mom?

04:20.993 --> 04:23.694
Can you hear that?

04:23.696 --> 04:25.062
It's...

04:25.064 --> 04:26.630
whispers.

04:26.632 --> 04:28.299
Saying a name.

04:28.301 --> 04:30.668
Over and over.

04:30.670 --> 04:33.304
Kre Nah Han...

04:33.306 --> 04:35.706
Kre Nah Han...

04:35.708 --> 04:37.408
Vincent, what...

04:37.410 --> 04:38.776
what is that?

04:38.778 --> 04:42.646
It's a nearly forgotten dialect.

04:42.648 --> 04:44.248
It's Creole.

04:44.250 --> 04:46.984
It means the Hollow.

04:46.986 --> 04:49.253
The Hollow is coming.

04:59.140 --> 05:03.887
